<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Resume Collection</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f06292; /* A vibrant pink color */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: white;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .resume-card {
            background-color: #f8bbd0; /* A lighter pink for the cards */
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            width: 200px;
        }

        .resume-card p {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #424242; /* Dark gray for text */
        }

        .resume-card a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .view-button {
            background-color: #e91e63; /* A strong pink for the button */
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .view-button:hover {
            background-color: #c2185b; /* A slightly darker pink on hover */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>My Resume Collection</h1>
        <div class="resume-collection-container">
            <div class="resume-card">
                <p>นางสาวอาจารย์อัญญารัตน์ ทองพักดี</p>
                <a href="path/to/resume1.pdf" target="_blank">
                    <button class="view-button">View</button>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-card">
                <p>นางสาวพจนมาลย์ นันท์จันทร์</p>
                <a href="path/to/resume2.pdf" target="_blank">
                    <button class="view-button">View</button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
